Content: [matrix] <cipig:matrix.org> problem is that canbind:1 only works if you have a public-IP, no NAT, and no firewall active

Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [matrix] <cipig:matrix.org> when "ifconfig" shows you a public IP, reachable from the internet, then you have a public IP, if it shows something like 192.168.x.x,. then you don't have a public IP. 99% of home internet does not have public IPs
